	<ul><li>Banisher Priest-like effects (When this card enters the battlefield, exile target creature/permanent until this card leaves play.)</li>
		<li>Blocking extra creatures (This creature can block an additional N creatures each combat.)</li>
		<li>Bring back creatures/permanents that went to the graveyard this turn</li>
		<li>Can't be attacked (Creatures can't attack you.)</li>
		<li>Destroy target attacking or blocking creature</li>
		<li>Destroy target creature that damaged you or a creature you control this turn</li>
		<li>Destroy target tapped creature</li>
		<li>Destroy target creature with power 4 or greater</li>
		<li>Destroy all creatures</li>
		<li>Destroy all creatures with power 4 or greater</li>
