		<li>+0/+N (on creatures)</li>
		<li>+0/+N (on spells)</li>
		<li>+0/+N (on Auras)</li>
		<li>+N/+N to your team, one-shot</li>
		<li>+0/+N to your team, one-shot</li>
		<li>+N/+N to your team, ongoing</li>
		<li>+0/+N to your team, ongoing</li>
		<li>Damage prevention (Prevent the next N damage that would be dealt to target creature/player.)</li>
		<li>Damage redirection (Prevent the next N damage that would be dealt to target creature/player this turn. If damage is prevented in this way, this card deals that much damage to target creature/player.)</li>
		<li>Defender</li>
		<li>Deal N damage to target attacking or blocking creature</li>
		<li>Double strike</li>
		<li>Enchantment destruction</li>
