		<li>Increasing counters and/or r\tokens</li>
		<li>"Lockdown" (Enchanted creature doesn't untap.)</li>
		<li>Looking at opponent's hand</li>
		<li>"Looting" (Draw a card and discard a card.)</li>
		<li>"Manipulate time" (End the turn.)</li>
		<li>"Maro" ability (This creature's power and toughness are equal to the number of cards in our hand.)</li>
		<li>"Milling" (Target player puts the top N cards from his or her library into his or her graveyard.)</li>
		<li>Moving enchantments/counters</li>
		<li>Playing cards off top of library</li>
